of <normalised orig="euery" auto="true">every</normalised> one, before they be admitted to the Lords
Supper.</head>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Question.<lb/>
WHat is the chiefest thing which <normalised orig="euery" auto="true">every</normalised> one ought<lb/>
to be most <normalised orig="carefull" auto="true">careful</normalised> of as long as they <normalised orig="liue" auto="true">live</normalised>?<lb/>
               </p>
