               <p>An. We can <normalised orig="neuer" auto="true">never</normalised> know how we be discharged before<lb/>
the <normalised orig="iudgement" auto="true">judgment</normalised> seat of God, <normalised orig="vntill" auto="true">until</normalised> such time as wee<lb/>
